  <scopecontent id="aspace_4746294d7fb8ea495205c4976ac24ba5">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Original fanzines, magazines, sound recordings, photographs, and posters documenting Black Metal music, including the production files for the book "True Norwegian black metal: we turn in the night consumed by fire" with photographs by Peter Beste.</p><p> 6 vinyl records by Ulver/Mysticum, Burzum, Abruptum, and Mayhem.</p>  </scopecontent>
